{"tid":341600,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我阿媽係一個清潔工","createTime":"2017-07-31T02:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T20:40:37.000Z","uid":77245,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d63de849626fd610e18c7c694a3997f94d37af9","tid":341600,"uid":77245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:14:56.000Z","msg":"阿媽做左清潔大約4年<br />\n每朝3點9起身 4點要打卡<br />\n下午3點3放工<br />\n每日就係掃球場 執垃圾 洗廁所<br />\n仲要搭車去送文件<br />\n<br />\n我係屋企最細 今年畢業出左黎做嘢<br />\n叫阿媽唔好再做<br />\n但佢又話無嘢做係屋企好悶<br />\n好似阿爸咁無嘢做日日係屋企瞓覺煲劇<br />\n試過叫佢參加工聯會嗰啲<br />\n佢又話我毒既性格係遺傳於佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢唔想出去識朋友 唔鍾意對人<br />\n<br />\n但近排發現佢曬到黑左好多<br />\n仲開始有駝背<br />\n連阿爸皮膚都好過阿媽了<br />\n本身家姐生左個bb話俾阿媽湊<br />\n阿媽都準備辭工<br />\n但最後bb嫲嫲辭工快一步<br />\nbb就俾左嫲嫲湊<br />\n阿媽就話繼續返工<br />\n做到郁唔到為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好矛盾 我唔想睇住阿媽再咁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日出糧 準備放工再去說服下阿媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26baed085aef8d8ad124f1583403f2c87f579ed","tid":341600,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:18:04.000Z","msg":"你每個月出糧比佢 叫佢打理好家頭細務咪得"},{"pid":"3ff1e47f6a656cbe50d62a970db90bb059c25424","tid":341600,"uid":31405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:18:44.000Z","msg":"如果啊媽真係咁想做野<br />\n叫佢去做保安好過啦<br />\n<br />\n洗廁所真係好辛苦"},{"pid":"5df7043e1ab95ab8e3122d606eb265e2fdfadb56","tid":341600,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:19:33.000Z","msg":"去做陪月都好"},{"pid":"55093a6c4ac7214c34d29d06417b9b0cc7bb96bd","tid":341600,"uid":120837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:22:23.000Z","msg":"如果唔係為錢，不如試下轉做鐘點或者寫字樓清潔姐姐？<br />\n有工返但又唔洗日曬雨淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e426f25e7f83650b5fc8bba7d9448c7e58f9791b","tid":341600,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"人地話左唔做野好悶<br />\n你叫佢唔做野「牛」係屋企咪仲慘"},{"pid":"8de90dc141e5a3a4b72c1de6fc75fbe19b8d8da8","tid":341600,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:28:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果啊媽真係咁想做野<br />\n叫佢去做保安好過啦<br />\n<br />\n洗廁所真係好辛苦</blockquote><br />\nagger, 樓主老母好辛苦，不如同樓主家姐奶奶針下，分返一兩日比樓主老母，比個籍口佢退休。。。"},{"pid":"51ada238d20e54b757b4a1449820cdc7186b72d6","tid":341600,"uid":1345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:29:00.000Z","msg":"見到佢咁辛苦 有時寧願自己辛苦啲都唔想佢再挨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f221c94b7e17d8f6a90e0f079818e656c4c4a5","tid":341600,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:29:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果唔係為錢，不如試下轉做鐘點或者<span style=\"color: red;\">寫字樓清潔姐姐</span>？<br />\n有工返但又唔洗日曬雨淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢啲通常一做就幾間，好少凈係做一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36696ab536cd9f73668e9b50c110cd3e08c74b32","tid":341600,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:31:20.000Z","msg":"同姨甥女的嫲嫲傾下"},{"pid":"5fe75d5991618458cd40c550de842077c522a6d7","tid":341600,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:32:49.000Z","msg":"有人牛命來<br />\n一唔做野好快身體變差死鳩埋"},{"pid":"b3a1e59ee634465bc4097471e9bd3b581950e37f","tid":341600,"uid":72045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:35:14.000Z","msg":"叫佢炒散嘛算囉，返下d酒店宴會，想做就返唔想做就係屋企玩bb"},{"pid":"46dda94917338f1f109aae9ac63815d2fbea3c73","tid":341600,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:37:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有人牛命來<br />\n一唔做野好快身體變差死鳩埋</blockquote><br />\n呢個真"},{"pid":"c28cf932f3fb5682d6d0b1f4a4cde45ca7a75c85","tid":341600,"uid":53272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:55:38.000Z","msg":"叫佢翻啲時間好啲既<br />\n同埋唔好翻全職<br />\n有好多只係翻3，4個鐘<br />\n<br />\n多啲同佢講話今晚想食乜食乜<br />\n陪佢一齊食飯<br />\n等佢就算翻pt都有啲野寄託<br />\n可以放多啲時間係屋企<br />\n<br />\n仲有仲有買頂防曬帽，防曬手套同買枝防曬<br />\n一定要佢帶同查下<br />\n人唔查防曬會老得好快<br />\n特別係呢排紫外線好毒<br />\n<br />\n你買比佢佢一定會好開心同用<br />\n<br />\n利申 翻工成日接觸清潔嬸嬸"},{"pid":"ceeb782345ecba07882a910bf7853814c9f5ffeb","tid":341600,"uid":67504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:57:16.000Z","msg":"叻仔！"},{"pid":"5e0d1046e2906052f3ccd73ef4e5c8dc84a6da0c","tid":341600,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:59:51.000Z","msg":"可以搵d時間無咁長嘅工做"},{"pid":"5a2ffd94688c2a8ac60c886757ca7039c9322514","tid":341600,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:00:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f0e8930fd22548caad1c2de0a37ed4efad957ad","tid":341600,"uid":46207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:09:52.000Z","msg":"我呀媽都係咁 我叫過佢好多次唔好做 唔想佢咁辛苦 但佢唔聽 話留係屋企無聊  不如去賺錢  不過佢好啲 工作時間唔長 每日好似返四個鐘 係幫屋企附近社區中心清潔下 <br />\n其實好難叫佢地唔做野 試下叫你呀媽揾份輕鬆啲做"},{"pid":"bb6274287e96ff831209a0a82c7d42965da36682","tid":341600,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:13:19.000Z","msg":"一係叫佢去茶餐廳執枱執凳做幾個鐘個d"},{"pid":"ea3c61b14d6623bee74d2b5f372cf14207be74bd","tid":341600,"uid":38884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:16:19.000Z","msg":"做保安"},{"pid":"d6d3fd87428f6b18058b1cddeaa9c784700738e5","tid":341600,"uid":77245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你每個月出糧比佢 叫佢打理好家頭細務咪得</blockquote><br />\n岩岩返左一個月工 今日出糧<br />\n今晚試下同佢傾"},{"pid":"616d7706fa7b49933f970298e7c14a1f99d37be9","tid":341600,"uid":77245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:51:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果啊媽真係咁想做野<br />\n叫佢去做保安好過啦<br />\n<br />\n洗廁所真係好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n揾下有無輕鬆少少工時無咁長既工<br />\n洗廁所真係好辛苦<br />\n啲人仲要亂咁痾<br />\n公園啲廁所係最臭"},{"pid":"db7e0574445c0d73e3251b627de5c75e62bb038b","tid":341600,"uid":77245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:52:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去做陪月都好</blockquote><br />\n不過媽無經驗 又60歲了<br />\n未必有人請"},{"pid":"4b8596fa3afd5499ff4df404ea0d8a7bede6b991","tid":341600,"uid":77245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:53:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果唔係為錢，不如試下轉做鐘點或者寫字樓清潔姐姐？<br />\n有工返但又唔洗日曬雨淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會開始揾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />寫字樓每日返幾個鐘都好<br />\n有啲嘢做又唔太辛苦"},{"pid":"61582fabe7b2508378ab7b00bdbe2f00ff76e5f6","tid":341600,"uid":77245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地話左唔做野好悶<br />\n你叫佢唔做野「牛」係屋企咪仲慘</blockquote><br />\n係呀 佢就係咁講 話就算放假一日係屋企都好悶"}]}